{"id":"a019","internalId":"99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22","createdAt":"2026-01-28T06:53:20.809Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-24T10:39:59.752Z","status":{"code":"PUBLISHED","name":"Published"},"assessmentType":{"code":"CAR_ASSISTED_DRIVING","name":"Car Assisted Driving"},"assessmentDiagrams":[],"publicationDate":"2024-10-23","publicationYear":"2024","ratingYear":2024,"SPRefNumber":"a019","umbracoRefNumber":null,"rescueSheetURL":null,"greenNcapURL":null,"frontalImageURL":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__d3c29c8e368a3f5b_original.png","frontalImage":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__d3c29c8e368a3f5b_original.png","altText":null,"width":1144,"height":760,"formats":{"large":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__59cbb47510179288_lg.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"small":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__20bea912740164e1_sm.webp","width":320,"height":213},"medium":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__098c1a0e6e16118f_md.webp","width":768,"height":510},"xlarge":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__59cbb47510179288_xl.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"thumbnail":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/99aa7319-ed32-44da-8270-728c20e29f22/Volvo-EC40__d57cbc2233f30449_thumb.webp","width":156,"height":104}}},"newsMarketURL":"https://news.euroncap.com/safercars/choose-a-car/volvo-ec40---euro-ncap-2024-assisted-driving-results---good-grading/s/fa952059-48c8-41d8-aa41-75c7780a78f2","resultApplicability":"all","comments":"<p>Volvo’s appropriately named Pilot Assist’ accurately portrays system functionality. The promotional material and the handbook correctly indicate the limitations of the system capabilities. System status information is clearly displayed but there is no head-up display in the EC40. The sensing of hands on the steering wheel was not robust, and the system lost points in this area. The system balances driver steering input with lane guidance, promoting co-operative driving.</p><p>The EC40 combines map-based speed limit information with real time camera inputs to manage fixed, variable and temporary speed limit signs but does not adapt speed for upcoming road features such as curves and junctions. The EC40 responds to avoid or mitigate a collision in many of the ACC test scenarios. The driver is supported through the S-Bend, but the car is kept fully in lane only at the lowest test speed. A lane-change assist function is not provided. In case of an unresponsive driver, the Volvo performs a controlled stop within lane. If the radar or camera is blocked the car provides a timely warning and prevents system activation.</p><p>The EC40 from Volvo provides good Vehicle Assistance with a similar level of Driver Engagement. Combined with a high level safety back-up, the system, overall, offers Good highway assistance.</p>","testedHandOfDrive":null,"assessmentTags":[],"assessmentData":{"carAssistedDriving":{"disclaimer":"When using Assisted Driving Systems (also known as SAE Level 2 systems), a driver’s responsibilities include monitoring the system’s control of speed, braking and steering at all times, strict compliance with traffic rules, and maintaining situational awareness throughout the journey. Certain situations might negatively influence the system’s performance (e.g. poor weather, faded lane markings, construction zones, exiting a tunnel), resulting in a sudden interruption of the lateral and/or longitudinal support (system disengagement). Moreover, the system may fail to detect certain road users such as motorcyclists not directly in front of the vehicle, or stationary objects. Appropriate fitness to drive is critical for safe travel, even when using Assisted Driving Systems. Visual distraction (e.g. eyes off the road), impairment (e.g. drowsiness, intoxication) as well as unresponsiveness, poses high risks. It is highly recommended to keep your hands on the steering wheel at all times to ensure immediate reaction when the system disengages.","domain":{"highway":"RECOMMENDED","interUrban":"RECOMMENDED","urban":"NOT_RECOMMENDED"},"nicePublicationDate":"October 2024","assistedDrivingPerformance":{"assistanceCompetence":{"score":66,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":66,"driverEngagement":{"score":66.5,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":66.5,"elements":{"consumerInformation":{"score":23,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"marketingMaterial":{"url":"https://www.volvocars.com/uk/support/topic/3dbb6473aa47d37dc0a8015175f7bdc6?search=pilot%20assist&page=0","viewDate":"14/10/2024"},"quickStartGuide":true,"handbook":{"url":"https://euroncap.blob.core.windows.net/media/83332/volvo-ec40-2024-a019_vehicle-handbook_driver-support.pdf"}}},"systemStatus":{"score":18.5,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"continuousSystemStatusIndicator":"GREEN","systemStatusChangeIndicator":"GREEN"}},"driverMonitoring":{"score":0,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"RED","elements":{"handsOnMonitoring":"RED","directDriverMonitoring":"RED"}},"drivingCollaboration":{"score":25,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"increaseSteeringTorque":"GREEN","overrideResponse":"GREEN","comment":"System continues to assist while driver steers to avoid obstacle"}}}},"vehicleAssistance":{"score":70.6,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":70.6,"elements":{"speedAssistance":{"score":18.2,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"speedAssistSystems":{"responseToFixedSpeedLimit":"At speed at sign","responseToVariableSpeedLimit":"Slowing down at sign"},"speedLimitInfoFunction":{"generalRequirements":"Compliant","conditionalSpeedLimits":"ORANGE","roadFeatures":"RED","localHazards":"RED","systemUpdates":"None"}}},"adaptiveCruiseControlPerformance":{"score":24.9,"maxScore":40,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"BROWN","motorCycle":"ORANGE"},"approachingSlowerMovingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"approachingBrakingTarget":{"car":"BROWN","motorCycle":"YELLOW"},"targetCuttingInFront":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"carCuttingOutFrontToExposeTarget":{"car":"YELLOW","motorCycle":"GREEN"}},"undertakePrevention":{"undertakePreventionSpeedOver90km":"RED"},"adaptiveCruiseControlAutoResume":{"assistanceMaintainedAfterFullStop":"GREEN","systemAssistanceMaintained":"Automatic resume within 5s of stop and driver input required over 5s"}}},"steeringAssistance":{"score":27.5,"maxScore":35,"verdict":"GREEN","laneChangeAssist":false,"scenarios":{"80km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"100km":{"verdict":"YELLOW","comment":"Vehicle directed in 2nd turn"},"120km":{"verdict":"YELLOW","comment":"Vehicle directed in 2nd turn"}}}}}},"safetyBackup":{"score":78,"normalisedScore":78,"elements":{"systemFailure":{"score":20,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","scenarios":{"sensorBlockedAtStartup":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemInactive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"After a 5 minute drive","warning":"After sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemActive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage within 2 minutes after blocking","warning":"After sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after sensor blocking","warning":"After sensor blocking"}}}},"unresponsiveDriverIntervention":{"score":20,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"